Package: coldchainfreight
Title: Distributed Monte Carlo Simulation for Cold-Chain Freight Emissions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Author", "Name", , "author@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Research-grade implementation of distributed Monte Carlo 
    simulation for comparing emissions from dry versus refrigerated freight 
    transport. Features deterministic models, chunk-based sampling, mergeable 
    histogram aggregation, exact moment merging, strict input validation, and 
    comprehensive reproducibility logging. Designed for offline operation with 
    no runtime API calls.
